result.adr_address: 6 Staunton St, Central, Hong Kong
result.name: Burger King

reviews.text: I was great.  Have not had a whopper in 3 years
Freshly cooked burgers and also serves beer (Asahi)

Oh yeah, burger King in hk is very very good, sounds unbelievable, but I was surprised about the really good burger. I got the whopper. Better than a lot of other more burgers place with bigger reputation. Actually I'll go again soon to confirm my toughts.
It is good as every Burger King you can find around the world so don't mind to check in. Service team is nice and friendly. Nothing to complain!

Definitely larger and better than McDonald’s, but also much more pricy.

The double cheeseburger is very small.  OMG
